贵，但架不住这里是凤朝的皇城，不缺官二代、富二代有钱的公子哥。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",1,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]官二代：啧啧，已经下贱至此了吗？六两是不是太贵了？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",3,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]铁匠：可恶，实在是有点贵，这可是俺的老婆本。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",3,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]乞丐：卧槽，我现在就找朋友凑钱。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]穿着黑袍的男子，对着其他人笑道。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]秦正经：过时不候，来来交钱就给大爷你们玩个够。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"47-KZKJLRH2",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]秦正经拍了拍\\n[1]的头，\\n[1]听话的看着她，感受脸附近肉棒传来的浓浓味道。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",1,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]官二代：卧槽，是这样玩吗？受不了，六两我给了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",3,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]乞丐：可恶我的钱还没弄到。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]似乎没听到众人的声音，毫不犹豫的将面前的肉棒含入口中。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"47-KZKJLRH3",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]吞吐着嘴里的肉棒，纤细柔软的小手左右摸索着一旁的肉棒。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]秦正经的肉棒被\\n[1]吞吐着，\\n[1]的脸红润，一双无神的眸子，樱桃小嘴被不断撑开。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]柔软的舌头不断上下，\\n[1]感受口腔里都是肉棒厚重的味道。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]秦正经：仙子看起高冷的不行，身姿又那么骚，只是轻轻教你一下，你就学会了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]秦正经：什么仙子，你呀，是真正的骚货，纯天然的鸡。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]：... ..."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]：（为什么，为什么会变成这样，为什么我会沦落至此。）"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]还没有想明白，嘴中秦正经的肉棒忽然变的更大更硬，并且开始在嘴里跳动。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]：（这是什么？不要，我... ...）"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]一股苦涩腥臭的液体冲入\\n[1]嘴里，\\n[1]想吐出去，但身体却熟练的吞吐进去。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"47-KZKJLRH4",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]一旁的男人也受不了，纷纷缴械投降，精液顺着手流下来。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]这种羞辱让\\n[1]不知所措，身体却被浓厚的男性气味刺激的不断颤抖。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]一边舔着，一边喘息着。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]秦正经:这么点就受不了了嘛？仙子，还有很多人在等着你。"]},{"code":221,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]众人不断的来来回回，\\n[1]嘴里满满的精液，肚子都微微鼓了起来，实在是吃不下了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]嘴巴，身躯，手上都是男人们精液的味道，\\n[1]从一开始的愤怒，抗拒，到最后迷茫，甚至高潮。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]还有人想继续，秦正经可不想玩具被弄坏，让众人一昏，带着\\n[1]离开。"]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[2]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":122,"indent":0,"parameters":[4,4,1,0,5]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]只感觉睡了一觉，迷迷糊糊的睁开双眼，已经是白天。"]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[652,652,1]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[18,18,1]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[53]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[9]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[325,325,1]},{"code":201,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,93,5,4,2,0]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":223,"indent":0,"parameters":[[0,0,0,0],60,false]},{"code":222,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":0,"stepAnime":false,"through":false,"trigger":3,"walkAnime":true}],"x":8,"y":3},
